14
00:03:10,030 --> 00:03:12,160
Taking a few hits for you is no big deal.

15
00:03:18,079 --> 00:03:19,360
Who is he?

16
00:03:20,710 --> 00:03:22,760
A scumbag who has to

17
00:03:23,800 --> 00:03:24,610
stay hidden.

18
00:03:33,200 --> 00:03:34,530
What happened to Ran Yi?

19
00:03:35,370 --> 00:03:37,310
Ran Yi was controlled by Li Lun.

20
00:03:37,890 --> 00:03:39,579
Weak demons

21
00:03:40,150 --> 00:03:42,550
are easily controlled by powerful demons.

22
00:03:44,460 --> 00:03:45,270
Zhu Yan,

23
00:03:47,030 --> 00:03:50,579
you're making worse and worse friends.

24
00:03:51,800 --> 00:03:55,640
At least, you used to interact with the Baize Goddess.

25
00:03:57,620 --> 00:03:58,590
Now,

26
00:03:58,590 --> 00:04:00,540
even these cheap things

27
