the name of her late brother, Zhao Yuanzhou.

32
00:04:20,709 --> 00:04:21,779
Zhu Yan.

33
00:04:23,470 --> 00:04:25,140
Am I right?

34
00:04:26,630 --> 00:04:29,240
One was the noble Baize Goddess.

35
00:04:29,670 --> 00:04:32,690
One was the evil great demon, Zhu Yan.

36
00:04:34,870 --> 00:04:36,600
Because he didn't want others to know

37
00:04:36,600 --> 00:04:38,430
they were close,

38
00:04:40,220 --> 00:04:41,670
every time

39
00:04:41,670 --> 00:04:44,390
he was with Zhao Wan'er,

40
00:04:45,990 --> 00:04:47,790
he would wear a mask.

41
00:04:52,510 --> 00:04:53,630
It really is you.

42
00:05:24,740 --> 00:05:26,020
Zhuo Yichen,

43
00:05:27,330 --> 00:05:29,520
don't you want to

44
00:05:30,190 --> 00:05:32,020
avenge your blood feud?

45
00:05:33,460 --> 00:05:35,680
Although he had no choice,

46
00:05:36,710 --> 00:05:40,110
he did kill your father and brother.

47
00:05:41,470 --> 00:05:43,690
If your dead father and brother

48
00:05:43,750 --> 00:05:47,060
saw you fighting alongside the enemy,

49
00:05:47,610 --> 00:05:49,420
how could they

50
00:05:51,180 --> 00:05:52,810
rest in peace?

51
00:05:56,680 --> 00:05:58,030
I can't kill him.

52
00:06:00,470 --> 00:06:01,830
You can.

53
00:06:04,050 --> 00:06:06,330
With my help,

54
00:06:07,570 --> 00:06:09,200
you can.

55
00:06:14,670 --> 00:06:15,560
Okay.

56
00:06:35,409 --> 00:06:38,720
Humans always love to lie.

57
00:06:38,830 --> 00:06:41,220
I will kill Zhao Yuanzhou.

58
00:06:42,250 --> 00:06:46,210
But first, I need to kill you, an even more evil thing.

59
00:06:47,350 --> 00:06:49,210
If you kill me,

60
00:06:50,770 --> 00:06:53,720
no one will know where the Baize Token is.

61
00:06:53,750 --> 00:06:56,210
You know the whereabouts of the Baize Token?

62
00:06:57,470 --> 00:06:59,790
On the night Zhao Wan'er died,

63
00:07:00,530 --> 00:07:02,080
I was sealed,

64
00:07:02,840 --> 00:07:05,800
but I was the only conscious person at the scene.

65
00:07:06,000 --> 00:07:08,600
Naturally, I saw where the Baize Token went.

66
00:07:10,040 --> 00:07:10,840
Where is it?

67
00:07:14,110 --> 00:07:16,030
It's on you.

68
00:07:20,590 --> 00:07:23,160
You saw it in your dream just now.

69
00:07:23,990 --> 00:07:25,160
Right?

70
00:07:32,900 --> 00:07:36,110
But now, you only have half of Baize Token,

71
00:07:37,159 --> 00:07:39,370
so you can’t use it.

72
00:07:39,710 --> 00:07:41,040
Where is the other half?

73
00:07:41,880 --> 00:07:43,270
Do you want to know?

74
00:07:48,150 --> 00:07:49,980
But I don't want to tell you.

75
00:07:51,150 --> 00:07:53,380
You have to say it anyway.

76
00:08:22,570 --> 00:08:25,170
Ran Yi's dream control magic is useless on him.

77
00:08:32,380 --> 00:08:33,720
Really?

78
00:08:46,150 --> 00:08:48,550
He has been running away for so long.

79
00:08:50,010 --> 00:08:50,710
Today,

80
00:08:50,710 --> 00:08:53,540
let him sink into it.

81
00:09:17,640 --> 00:09:18,440
Zhuo!

82
00:10:06,610 --> 00:10:07,410
Chen.

83
00:10:10,210 --> 00:10:12,110
Today is the Double Third Festival.

84
00:10:12,110 --> 00:10:13,910
Why are you still practicing?

85
00:10:14,150 --> 00:10:16,370
I want to practice my swordsmanship

86
00:10:16,510 --> 00:10:19,150
and help Father and Brother in the future.

87
00:10:20,140 --> 00:10:21,610
The Double Third Festival

88
00:10:22,570 --> 00:10:24,010
is not that fun.

89
00:10:26,310 --> 00:10:28,600
I still remember when you were seven,

90
00:10:29,240 --> 00:10:30,640
you came crying

91
00:10:30,750 --> 00:10:31,950
to complain to me

92
00:10:32,790 --> 00:10:34,050
that the others

93
00:10:34,110 --> 00:10:35,970
weren't willing to play with you.

94
00:10:36,550 --> 00:10:38,150
Because your father

95
00:10:38,350 --> 00:10:39,240
and brother

96
00:10:39,640 --> 00:10:41,500
were anomalies who hunted demons

97
00:10:42,270 --> 00:10:44,220
and dealt with demons all the time.

98
00:10:44,790 --> 00:10:46,060
One day,

99
00:10:46,090 --> 00:10:47,890
they would turn into demons too.

100
00:10:50,390 --> 00:10:51,180
Brother,

101
00:10:51,980 --> 00:10:54,310
you still remember the nonsense I said

102
00:10:54,950 --> 00:10:56,190
when I was a kid?

103
00:10:57,380 --> 00:10:59,260
But after so many years,

104
00:11:01,270 --> 00:11:03,400
you indeed haven't made many friends.

105
00:11:04,680 --> 00:11:06,420
You're always alone.

106
00:11:10,740 --> 00:11:11,550
Brother.

107
00:11:14,750 --> 00:11:15,910
Did I

108
00:11:19,020 --> 00:11:21,620
turn myself into an anomaly?

109
00:11:24,120 --> 00:11:25,320
So-called anomalies

110
00:11:26,390 --> 00:11:28,510
are just what narrow-minded people say

111
00:11:28,510 --> 00:11:30,250
in order to team up together

112
00:11:30,510 --> 00:11:33,110
and bring others down.

113
00:11:33,870 --> 00:11:34,860
They use this

114
00:11:35,070 --> 00:11:36,990
to show their righteousness

115
00:11:37,390 --> 00:11:39,650
and hide their own inferiority complex.

116
00:11:40,550 --> 00:11:41,110
Chen,

117
00:11:42,300 --> 00:11:43,780
we were born with

118
00:11:43,800 --> 00:11:45,530
different responsibilities,

119
00:11:46,000 --> 00:11:47,920
so we are destined to bear

120
00:11:47,990 --> 00:11:50,320
the pain that ordinary people don't have.

121
00:11:52,230 --> 00:11:52,760
Brother.

122
00:11:55,510 --> 00:11:57,230
Did you live like this too?

123
00:12:05,150 --> 00:12:06,310
Do you get lonely?

124
00:12:09,140 --> 00:12:10,600
Maybe one day,

125
00:12:12,320 --> 00:12:13,430
you will meet someone

126
00:12:13,430 --> 00:12:15,550
you see as an anomaly.

127
00:12:17,150 --> 00:12:20,010
At that time, you'll need to make your own judgment.

128
00:12:20,630 --> 00:12:22,430
Your eyes lie.

129
00:12:23,590 --> 00:12:24,660
But your heart

130
00:12:24,870 --> 00:12:26,270
will tell you the answer.

131
00:12:30,390 --> 00:12:31,630
I believe you

132
00:12:32,230 --> 00:12:35,110
will surely meet like-minded companions.

133
00:12:36,230 --> 00:12:37,070
By then,

134
00:12:37,550 --> 00:12:39,150
you won't be lonely anymore.

135
00:12:43,950 --> 00:12:44,950
Will that happen?

136
00:12:46,750 --> 00:12:47,840
Of course.

137
00:12:50,390 --> 00:12:51,200
Remember,

138
00:12:52,950 --> 00:12:54,280
one wing is hard to keep.

139
00:12:55,340 --> 00:12:56,970
With two wings, you can soar.

140
00:13:41,850 --> 00:13:42,640
Zhuo!

141
00:14:19,940 --> 00:14:20,850
Zhuo!

142
00:14:22,470 --> 00:14:24,450
Zhuo!

143
00:15:22,070 --> 00:15:23,110
Wen Xiao!

144
00:15:56,960 --> 00:15:57,750
Zhuo Yichen!

145
00:15:58,200 --> 00:15:59,160
Wake up!

146
00:16:00,630 --> 00:16:03,030
The Cloud Light Sword can kill demons and destroy evil

147
00:16:03,030 --> 00:16:04,260
without being tainted by demons.

148
00:16:04,260 --> 00:16:05,750
It can break through

149
00:16:05,750 --> 00:16:07,450
all demonic hallucinations.

150
00:16:30,230 --> 00:16:31,450
He can't be woken up.

151
00:16:33,190 --> 00:16:34,790
Because he has never

152
00:16:34,820 --> 00:16:37,400
truly faced his nightmare.

153
00:16:38,060 --> 00:16:39,820
All these years,

154
00:16:40,390 --> 00:16:43,180
he has never had a dream.

155
00:16:44,840 --> 00:16:49,260
So he can't tell if it's a dream or not.

156
00:16:52,080 --> 00:16:54,550
He won't wake up.

157
00:16:56,910 --> 00:16:58,000
Zhuo!

158
00:18:19,030 --> 00:18:20,510
Zhuo Yichen.

159
00:18:22,570 --> 00:18:24,980
If I'm your nightmare,

160
00:18:29,100 --> 00:18:31,740
then pierce me.

161
00:19:07,950 --> 00:19:09,430
My nightmare

162
00:19:11,000 --> 00:19:12,430
isn't you.

163
00:19:20,430 --> 00:19:22,230
It's myself.

164
00:19:28,390 --> 00:19:30,540
I'm afraid of dreaming

165
00:19:31,720 --> 00:19:32,980
and don't have dreams,

166
00:19:35,950 --> 00:19:37,880
so after my brother died,

167
00:19:38,670 --> 00:19:40,710
I never saw him in my dreams again.

168
00:19:44,780 --> 00:19:46,410
What I must overcome

169
00:19:48,430 --> 00:19:50,830
is myself, who has always been running away

170
00:19:52,470 --> 00:19:54,640
and has always been cowardly.

171
00:20:07,150 --> 00:20:08,720
My nightmare

172
00:20:09,230 --> 00:20:10,460
is myself!

173
00:20:09,980 --> 00:20:16,000
♫Someday I'll return to my old hometown♫

174
00:20:16,840 --> 00:20:22,880
♫Wearing old clothes but with eyes shining bright♫

