00:20:23,850 --> 00:20:25,840
♫Holding brilliance in the right hand♫

176
00:20:25,880 --> 00:20:27,800
♫Biting down on all panic♫

177
00:20:27,820 --> 00:20:29,300
♫Wiping away frost with the left hand♫

178
00:20:29,340 --> 00:20:31,150
♫I finally look up♫

179
00:20:31,180 --> 00:20:34,030
♫You're in front of me♫

180
00:20:34,920 --> 00:20:37,080
♫Blocking the pain♫

181
00:20:50,720 --> 00:20:55,780
♫Heartlessness births a dream♫

