00:21:01,300 --> 00:21:03,190
There's no way out of this vast sea

184
00:21:03,210 --> 00:21:05,110
but is in the mortal world.

185
00:21:05,260 --> 00:21:08,150
The galaxy is slim and we hold hands.

186
00:21:08,740 --> 00:21:10,860
Travel together in the world.

187
00:21:10,950 --> 00:21:12,060
Break!

