00:21:40,070 --> 00:21:40,950
Ran Yi.

190
00:21:43,940 --> 00:21:44,870
Ran Yi.

191
00:21:45,310 --> 00:21:46,230
Ran Yi!

192
00:21:51,540 --> 00:21:52,590
Ran Yi.

193
00:21:55,700 --> 00:21:57,600
Miss Qi.

194
00:21:58,650 --> 00:21:59,710
Ran Yi.

195
00:22:02,870 --> 00:22:03,590
No.

196
00:22:08,060 --> 00:22:09,170
Ran Yi.

197
00:22:35,390 --> 00:22:37,530
She has been parasitized for too long.

198
00:22:38,400 --> 00:22:39,880
Her internal organs

199
00:22:40,520 --> 00:22:43,450
have been corroded by the malicious energy of Li Lun.

200
00:23:29,110 --> 00:23:30,150
Ran Yi.

201
00:23:33,110 --> 00:23:34,670
Do you remember

202
00:23:36,030 --> 00:23:39,410
the first time we met?

203
00:23:40,180 --> 00:23:41,310
Master,

204
00:23:41,430 --> 00:23:44,560
someone took down the notice of your search for famous doctors

205
00:23:44,560 --> 00:23:46,370
and said he can cure the lady's illness.

206
00:23:46,370 --> 00:23:47,210
But he...

207
00:23:47,480 --> 00:23:48,990
He's a little strange.

208
00:24:12,740 --> 00:24:14,740
When we first met,

209
00:24:15,630 --> 00:24:16,920
you covered your face

210
00:24:17,030 --> 00:24:18,780
with fabric

211
00:24:19,500 --> 00:24:21,630
and only revealed your eyes.

212
00:24:24,140 --> 00:24:26,690
But I will always remember

213
00:24:27,020 --> 00:24:28,620
those eyes.

214
00:24:29,930 --> 00:24:31,580
They were like

215
00:24:31,630 --> 00:24:34,490
a lake under the moonlit night sky.

216
00:24:34,950 --> 00:24:36,060
So beautiful.

217
00:24:40,510 --> 00:24:41,160
No.

218
00:24:44,570 --> 00:24:46,200
That wasn't the first time.

219
00:24:58,950 --> 00:24:59,750
My Lady,

220
00:24:59,880 --> 00:25:01,960
why do you always come to the lake?

221
00:25:04,380 --> 00:25:05,780
The books say,

222
00:25:06,710 --> 00:25:08,390
"All rivers return to the sea

223
00:25:08,740 --> 00:25:10,740
and all water returns to the abyss."

224
00:25:12,710 --> 00:25:14,630
But look at this lake.

225
00:25:15,590 --> 00:25:17,790
It's always trapped deep in the forest.

226
00:25:18,460 --> 00:25:20,910
Do you think it can return to the sea?

227
00:25:25,100 --> 00:25:26,360
Who's there?

228
00:25:30,860 --> 00:25:33,460
I was being chased by a demon hunter at the time.

229
00:25:33,760 --> 00:25:35,390
I was severely injured

230
00:25:35,980 --> 00:25:37,840
and was drifting along the water.

231
00:25:39,020 --> 00:25:40,480
In a daze,

232
00:25:41,470 --> 00:25:42,820
I saw you.

233
00:25:57,830 --> 00:25:59,960
I mustered all my strength

234
00:26:00,630 --> 00:26:01,720
to open my eyes

235
00:26:01,750 --> 00:26:03,150
and see you.

236
00:26:04,230 --> 00:26:07,440
You were like the legendary goddess of the Wilderness.

237
00:26:07,860 --> 00:26:09,510
Your eyes were gentle

238
00:26:09,750 --> 00:26:11,090
and compassionate.

239
00:26:11,920 --> 00:26:12,910
Go on.

240
00:26:14,990 --> 00:26:15,920
Go on.

241
00:26:19,730 --> 00:26:20,470
At that time,

242
00:26:20,470 --> 00:26:21,670
I told myself

243
00:26:23,160 --> 00:26:25,070
I must see you again.

244
00:26:27,070 --> 00:26:29,160
You've swum to many places.

245
00:26:29,870 --> 00:26:32,530
You must have seen a lot of beautiful sceneries.

246
00:26:36,520 --> 00:26:38,280
You're so silly.

247
00:26:39,620 --> 00:26:41,680
You've recovered,

248
00:26:43,610 --> 00:26:45,650
but you still refuse to leave.

249
00:26:47,430 --> 00:26:48,550
You can swim

250
00:26:48,570 --> 00:26:50,460
freely in the world,

251
00:26:51,030 --> 00:26:52,630
but you insist on

252
00:26:53,930 --> 00:26:56,160
being trapped in this cage with me.

253
00:27:19,590 --> 00:27:21,580
The sea is vast.

254
00:27:22,230 --> 00:27:24,020
There's no way out,

255
00:27:25,470 --> 00:27:27,230
but it is in the mortal world.

256
00:27:30,600 --> 00:27:33,360
I remember everything you said,

257
00:27:35,090 --> 00:27:37,590
the scenery you wanted to see,

258
00:27:38,160 --> 00:27:40,880
and all kinds of life you wanted to experience.

259
00:27:41,910 --> 00:27:44,210
So from then on,

260
00:27:45,610 --> 00:27:46,510
every night,

261
00:27:46,510 --> 00:27:48,710
I created a dream for you,

262
00:27:49,420 --> 00:27:51,820
so that the wishes you couldn't fulfill

263
00:27:51,910 --> 00:27:53,640
when trapped behind high walls

264
00:27:54,270 --> 00:27:55,630
could come true.

265
00:28:10,120 --> 00:28:12,650
I was willing to be with you forever like this,

266
00:28:13,270 --> 00:28:15,320
even if I had to abandon my freedom

267
00:28:15,760 --> 00:28:18,570
and just be a fish in your fish tank.

268
00:28:21,030 --> 00:28:22,470
But dream control magic

269
00:28:23,110 --> 00:28:24,570
is demonic, after all.

270
00:28:25,790 --> 00:28:28,320
The longer a person stays in a dream,

271
00:28:28,470 --> 00:28:30,030
the weaker one becomes.

272
00:28:30,070 --> 00:28:32,230
I couldn't create dreams for you anymore.

273
00:28:32,230 --> 00:28:33,420
Master.

274
00:28:33,440 --> 00:28:35,620
The lady is still not getting better.

275
00:28:35,870 --> 00:28:37,000
These past few days,

276
00:28:37,020 --> 00:28:38,520
she's become bedridden.

277
00:28:40,760 --> 00:28:42,990
That's why I became a doctor

278
00:28:43,390 --> 00:28:44,680
to accompany you.

279
00:28:46,950 --> 00:28:48,270
I drew,

280
00:28:49,830 --> 00:28:50,750
wrote,

281
00:28:51,780 --> 00:28:53,320
[Classic of Mountains and Seas]

282
00:28:51,950 --> 00:28:53,300
read travel books,

283
00:28:54,740 --> 00:28:57,200
and talked about the world outside with you.

284
00:28:58,030 --> 00:28:59,670
My favorite phrase

285
00:29:01,750 --> 00:29:03,350
is "dreams come true."

286
00:29:06,650 --> 00:29:08,220
When I say it,

287
00:29:10,550 --> 00:29:12,110
I feel so happy.

288
00:29:15,480 --> 00:29:17,280
Whether you are a human

289
00:29:17,300 --> 00:29:18,710
or a demon,

290
00:29:21,160 --> 00:29:23,080
you are both my path

291
00:29:24,210 --> 00:29:25,490
and destination.

